Product description

FC Barcelona home shirt from the 23/24 season.

- Nike Dri-FIT technology
- High-stretch, quick-drying fabric
- 100% polyester
- Colour: Blue and scarlet.

The delivery timeframe for personalized products is 7 to 14 days.
This product cannot be exchanged or returned.

*Player numbers will not be finalised until the transfer window closes. Barça Licensing and Merchandising (BLM) is not responsible for any changes occurring before shirt numbers for the upcoming 23/24 season are made official.

The 23/24 home kit brings back the classic shirts with the original wide blue and garnet stripes, including a diamond-shaped relief on the crest as an added detail, representing the first women’s team in history that played a football match at Camp Nou. The aim of this detail is to give visibility to one of the pillars that makes Barça a one-of-a-kind organisation on a global level—being at the forefront of everything we do. Just like our athletes in the past, FC Barcelona’s young players continue to be leaders who have been chosen to lead the way for the Club in the upcoming years.

Composition and care
100% Polyester. Machine wash at 40ºC max.
Size and adjustment
Standard fit.
Delivery and return
Free standard shipping in Spain over € 99.99. The delivery period for personalised products is 7 to 14 days. You will have 30 days to return any items, calculated from the date of confirmation of the delivery of the product(s).
